<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="csrf-token" content="<%= csrfToken %>">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <script src="/js/mission-assurance-module.js" defer></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div
        class="container mt-5 mb-5"
        id="mission-assurance-module-root"
        data-mission-assurance-overview-endpoint="/api/mission-assurance/overview"
        data-mission-assurance-evaluate-endpoint="/api/mission-assurance/evaluate">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4 flex-wrap gap-3">
            <div>
                <h1 class="notes-title mb-1">Mission Assurance Module</h1>
                <p class="text-muted mb-2">A research workspace for CAF-style tactical authentication and authorization, built around least privilege, RBAC, ABAC, server-side policy decisions, and auditable access control.</p>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Use the module to inspect the current session profile, compare mission roles against resource classifications, and simulate whether an action should be allowed before it touches a sensitive workflow.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <a href="/research" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Back to Research</a>
                <a href="/security/module" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Open Security Module</a>
                <a href="/ml/module" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Open ML Module</a>
                <a href="/notes" class="btn btn-secondary">Back to Notes</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                <div class="card research-summary-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="research-kicker mb-2">Mission Role</p>
                        <p class="display-6 mb-1" id="mission-assurance-role">-</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">RBAC baseline for the active session.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                <div class="card research-summary-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="research-kicker mb-2">Clearance</p>
                        <p class="display-6 mb-1" id="mission-assurance-clearance">-</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Highest classification the active profile may access.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                <div class="card research-summary-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="research-kicker mb-2">Assigned Missions</p>
                        <p class="display-6 mb-1" id="mission-assurance-missions">0</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Mission bindings available to the active profile.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                <div class="card research-summary-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="research-kicker mb-2">Allowed Decisions</p>
                        <p class="display-6 mb-1" id="mission-assurance-sensitive-count">0</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Policy decisions that are currently allowed in the matrix.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card automation-card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column flex-xl-row justify-content-between align-items-xl-center gap-3">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="h5 mb-1">Tactical Access Controls</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-1">This module treats authentication as only the first gate. Final access depends on an RBAC baseline plus ABAC context from role, clearance, mission assignment, device trust, network zone, and step-up MFA state.</p>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">The goal is not just to verify that a button works, but to verify whether the current identity should be allowed to use it inside a hardened operational system.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                    <button type="button" id="mission-assurance-refresh-btn" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Refresh Module</button>
                    <button type="button" id="mission-assurance-evaluate-btn" class="btn btn-dark">Evaluate Decision</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body pt-0">
                <div id="mission-assurance-status"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 mb-4">
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Principles</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Policy Baseline</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">These principles translate least-privilege military thinking into application-layer access control.</p>
                        <div id="mission-assurance-principles" class="row g-3"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Controls</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Recommended Hardening Controls</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">These controls turn policy theory into enforcement, evidence, and operational review.</p>
                        <div id="mission-assurance-controls" class="row g-3"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 mb-4">
            <div class="col-xl-5">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Profile</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Current Session Context</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">This is the normalized access profile the server is evaluating right now.</p>
                        <div id="mission-assurance-profile"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-7">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Matrix</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Decision Matrix</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">A quick allow or deny view across the most operationally sensitive action and resource pairs.</p>
                        <div id="mission-assurance-matrix"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card automation-card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <span class="research-kicker">Evaluator</span>
                <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Policy Decision</h2>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-3">Pick a persona, action, resource, and network zone to see how the policy engine reaches an allow or deny decision.</p>
                <form id="mission-assurance-form" class="row g-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label for="mission-assurance-persona-select" class="form-label">Persona</label>
                        <select id="mission-assurance-persona-select" class="form-select">
                            <option value="">Loading personas...</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label for="mission-assurance-action-select" class="form-label">Action</label>
                        <select id="mission-assurance-action-select" class="form-select">
                            <option value="">Loading actions...</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label for="mission-assurance-resource-select" class="form-label">Resource</label>
                        <select id="mission-assurance-resource-select" class="form-select">
                            <option value="">Loading resources...</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label for="mission-assurance-network-select" class="form-label">Network Zone</label>
                        <select id="mission-assurance-network-select" class="form-select">
                            <option value="corp">Corp</option>
                            <option value="mission">Mission</option>
                            <option value="public">Public</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <label for="mission-assurance-justification" class="form-label">Justification</label>
                        <textarea
                            id="mission-assurance-justification"
                            class="form-control"
                            rows="3"
                            placeholder="Add a justification when simulating break-glass or exceptional mission access."></textarea>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-xl-4">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center gap-3 mb-3 flex-wrap">
                            <div>
                                <span class="research-kicker">Result</span>
                                <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Decision Outcome</h2>
                            </div>
                            <span class="badge text-bg-light" id="mission-assurance-decision-badge">Awaiting evaluation</span>
                        </div>
                        <div id="mission-assurance-decision-summary"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-4">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Checks</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Policy Checks</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">Each decision is broken into explicit server-side gates so the denial path is reviewable.</p>
                        <div id="mission-assurance-checks"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-4">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Audit</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Required Follow-Up</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">When a sensitive action is allowed, the policy still imposes evidence and review obligations.</p>
                        <div id="mission-assurance-obligations"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
